query: SELECT COUNT(transaction_id) FROM Financial_Transactions JOIN Customers_Cards ON Customers_Cards.card_id = Financial_Transactions.card_id WHERE transaction_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND other_transaction_details = (SELECT MIN(other_transaction_details) FROM Financial_Transactions WHERE card_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT w.transaction_date) FROM Financial_Transactions AS w WHERE  w.transaction_amount > 92 LIMIT 1

SELECT Customers.customer_id, Customers.customer_address FROM Customers JOIN Customers AS y ON Customers.customer_id = y.customer_id WHERE  Customers.customer_id != 53 ORDER BY Customers.customer_id ASC LIMIT 4
SELECT customer_email, customer_address FROM Customers WHERE  customer_id <= 21 GROUP BY customer_address HAVING AVG(customer_id) < 59
SELECT COUNT(customer_id), COUNT(DISTINCT card_type_code) FROM Customers_Cards WHERE  customer_id < 95 LIMIT 4
SELECT customer_id, card_id, other_card_details FROM Customers_Cards WHERE  card_id >= 3 LIMIT 10
SELECT transaction_type, transaction_type FROM Financial_Transactions WHERE  transaction_amount = 28
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT other_customer_details) FROM Customers WHERE  customer_id < 47
SELECT COUNT(p.customer_id), p.card_number FROM Customers_Cards AS p
SELECT y.other_account_details, y.account_name FROM Accounts AS y WHERE account_id IN (SELECT account_id FROM Financial_Transactions AS m WHERE  m.transaction_id <= 87) GROUP BY y.account_name
SELECT account_name FROM Financial_Transactions JOIN Accounts ON Financial_Transactions.account_id = Accounts.account_id ORDER BY account_name DESC LIMIT 6

SELECT v.customer_email, v.customer_phone, v.customer_address FROM Customers JOIN Customers AS v ON Customers.customer_id = v.customer_id WHERE  v.customer_id < 69 GROUP BY v.customer_phone HAVING SUM(Customers.customer_id) = 35 ORDER BY v.customer_address ASC
SELECT transaction_type FROM Financial_Transactions WHERE  transaction_id = 88
SELECT customer_id FROM Accounts WHERE  customer_id = 9
SELECT MIN(account_id), customer_id, other_account_details FROM Accounts GROUP BY other_account_details

SELECT Accounts.account_id, card_type_code FROM Financial_Transactions JOIN Customers_Cards JOIN Accounts ON Financial_Transactions.account_id = Accounts.account_id AND Customers_Cards.card_id = Financial_Transactions.card_id ORDER BY Accounts.account_id DESC
SELECT o.customer_id, o.customer_phone FROM Customers AS o WHERE  o.customer_id < 96 ORDER BY o.customer_id DESC LIMIT 3
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT customer_id) FROM Accounts WHERE  account_id <= 6
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT other_account_details), other_transaction_details FROM Financial_Transactions JOIN Accounts ON Financial_Transactions.account_id = Accounts.account_id
SELECT MIN(e.card_id), e.customer_id FROM Customers_Cards AS e WHERE  e.card_id > 39 ORDER BY e.customer_id ASC
SELECT MIN(transaction_amount), transaction_type FROM Financial_Transactions WHERE  account_id != 99 ORDER BY transaction_type ASC LIMIT 7

SELECT v.customer_id FROM Customers AS v WHERE v.customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR customer_first_name NOT IN (SELECT customer_first_name FROM Customers WHERE  customer_id < 73) ORDER BY v.customer_id DESC

SELECT transaction_amount, transaction_id FROM Financial_Transactions WHERE account_id IN (SELECT account_id FROM Financial_Transactions WHERE previous_transaction_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  account_id > 75 LIMIT 9) ORDER BY transaction_id DESC

SELECT other_account_details, account_name FROM Financial_Transactions JOIN Accounts ON Financial_Transactions.account_id = Accounts.account_id WHERE  previous_transaction_id >= 4 ORDER BY other_account_details DESC

SELECT customer_id, other_account_details FROM Accounts WHERE  customer_id > 57 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Financial_Transactions AS l WHERE l.transaction_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  l.transaction_id >= 60 AND Accounts.account_id = l.account_id LIMIT 6) GROUP BY customer_id HAVING SUM(customer_id) > 78
SELECT COUNT(n.customer_id) FROM Customers AS n WHERE  n.customer_id = 66 LIMIT 10
SELECT customer_id, customer_id FROM Customers_Cards WHERE  card_id != 70 AND customer_id IN (SELECT customer_id FROM Customers_Cards AS s WHERE s.customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 6)
SELECT r.transaction_comment FROM Financial_Transactions AS r

SELECT v.card_id, v.card_id, v.card_type_code, v.date_valid_from FROM Customers_Cards AS v WHERE v.customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY v.date_valid_from HAVING AVG(v.customer_id) = 56 ORDER BY v.date_valid_from DESC LIMIT 5
